`,qe(t.p,{children:qe(t.em,{children:"Figure 2. Overview of the EmoMM construction pipeline: data curation for CH-SIMS v2.0 and CMU-MOSI, single-modality human labeling for independent unimodal annotations on CMU-MOSI (CH-SIMS v2.0 provides unimodal labels), followed by statistical analysis and subset partitioning under sentiment conflicts and modality missingness."})}),`
